Class LSQR.PartialResult

java.lang.Object
gov.sandia.gmp.util.numerical.matrix.LSQR.PartialResult
Enclosing class:
LSQR
public class LSQR.PartialResult extends Object
A dummy CompletionService result class returned to the caller after each task is finished. The result contains the row/column start/stop values for each task.
